<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA12">
<l>pallāṇ ṭeṉṟu pavittira ṉaippara mēṭṭiyai cārṅkameṉṉum</l>
<l>villāṇ ṭāṉṟaṉṉai villipput tūrviṭṭu cittaṉ virumpiyacol</l>
<l>nallāṇ ṭeṉṟu naviṉṟuraip pārnamō nārāya ṇāyaveṉṟu</l>
<l>pallāṇ ṭumpara mātmaṉaic cūḻntirun tēttuvar pallāṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who say the loving words of Viṭṭu Cittaṉ of Villiputtūr,</l>
<l>saying “many years” to the Pure One,</l>
<l rend="indent">the Supreme Being, to him, the Master of every bow-string and bow,</l>
<l>uttering “good year,” saying “Namo Nārāyaṇāya,”</l>
<l>and circumambulating the Supreme Soul with “many years”,</l>
<l>they will [get to] praise [Him] with “many years”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
